dct_description_sm: United States Coast Survey ; triangulation by A.D. Bache ... [et al.] ; topography by F.W. Dorr, W.H. Dennis ... ; hydrography by E. Cordell ... [et al.] ; verification of hydrography by C.P. Patterson.
Depths shown by isolines, shading, and soundings.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Soundings are expressed in feet... and fathoms..."
"Issued in June 1878 C.P. Patterson Superintendent ; verified J.E. Hilgard, Assistant in charge of Office."
Includes charts for lights and tides.
